featured_reviews.review_translated_text: This is the Eidgah where Muslims pray.. Muslims pray here every day during Ramadan.. There is a square enclosure.. The two pillars which are usually in front of the shrines are preserved in front.. Maybe they were used to light the lamps.. Next to it is Pochamma Gudi.. Behind it is a pond.
